# OpenWeatherMap API key — https://openweathermap.org/api
# Requires a One Call API 4.0 subscription (paid, separate from the free tier).
#
# Development (.env file, loaded automatically by Nuxt):
OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
#
# Production (runtime override, no rebuild needed):
# Set NUXT_OPEN_WEATHER_API_KEY in your hosting environment instead.
# Nuxt reads NUXT_<KEY> vars at startup and overrides the matching runtimeConfig value.
$PNPM_PATH=